; OpDecorate minimum = 3 (header + target + decoration); WordCount=1 is
; malformed.
; Test that malformed input is rejected early rather than silently causing
; integer underflow and potential process hang.
;
; With the fix, SPIRVCK exits immediately before any allocation.
; ulimit is not required but can be added as a safety net on non-Windows platforms:
;   RUNx: %if !system-windows %{ ulimit -v 1048576 %}

; RUN: not llvm-spirv %s -to-binary -o %t.spv 2>&1 | FileCheck %s
; CHECK: InvalidWordCount:

119734787 65536 0 6 0
2 Capability Kernel
3 MemoryModel 1 2
1 Decorate 5 RelaxedPrecision
